				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$|\eta |$$\end{document}.

The photon identification criteria were first optimised prior to the start of the data-taking in 2010, on simulated samples of prompt photons from γ+\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
